Thorch source license
=========================

Unless a file says otherwise, Thorch-specific source code, packaging recipes,
build scripts, installer scripts, configuration, and documentation in this
repository are licensed under the GNU General Public License version 2 or later:

SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0-or-later

Thorch builds images from third-party upstream projects and imported
artifacts. Those inputs keep their own licenses, notices, and provenance. In
particular, imported Linux kernel artifacts, Arch Linux ARM packages, ROCKNIX
firmware, FEX, KDE, Valve/Steam payloads fetched by user opt-in installers, and
device/vendor names are not relicensed by this repository.
